# ScrollArea — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/scroll-area.css`

## CSS Classes

### Structure
- `.acko-scroll-area` — smooth scroll, thin scrollbar, semantic colors

### Orientation (via `.acko-scroll-area-{vertical|horizontal|both}`)
| Orientation | Overflow |
|-------------|----------|
| vertical | overflow-y: auto; overflow-x: hidden |
| horizontal | overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: hidden |
| both | overflow: auto |

### Scrollbar (design tokens)
- Firefox: scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-border) transparent
- WebKit: width/height var(--scale-6), thumb var(--color-border), thumb:hover var(--color-border-strong), border-radius var(--radius-full)
